<title>
Windshield Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A9506001">Windshield Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9506002001">
<title>
Preparation
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.479in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.708in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Item to be prepared
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Usage
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Eyeleteer
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Drilling hole in adhesive
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Piano string and wood stick (or commercial windshield knife)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Cutting adhesive
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Knife
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To cut off adhesive for finishing
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
White gasoline and gauze
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To degrease and clean adhesive surface
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Caulking gun
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To apply adhesive
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Rubber sucker grip
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To hold glass
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Adhesive (Yokohama Rubber WS-212 or equivalent)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To bond glass
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Primer for glass (Yokohama rubber MS-90S or equivalent)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To pretreat adhesive surface
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Primer for adhesive surface (Yokohama rubber RC-50E or equivalent)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To pretreat adhesive surface
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Masking tape
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Protection against scratch
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Alcohol
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To degrease knife
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Adhesive tape
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
To secure windshield molding
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9506002002" page = "2">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clean inside, outside and around glass.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove wiper arms. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9406003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove cowl top garnish. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using masking tape, cover body surface around glass to prevent any damage when cutting the adhesive.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove inner rear view mirror. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9506007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove instrument panel, if necessary. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove roof lining, if necessary. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove or cut windshield molding.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Make hole into adhesive with eyeleteer (1) and pass piano string through it.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01950040.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.169mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Cut all adhesives of windshield (1) with piano string (2).
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Do not damage windshield when using windshield knife (3) to cut adhesive.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Use piano string as close as possible to glass to prevent damage to body and instrument panel.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH0A950006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "96.762mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "257"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using knife (1), smoothen adhesive remaining (2) on body side (3) and thickness of adhesive should be 1 to 2 mm (0.04 to 0.07 in.).
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
If windshield is to be reused, be careful to remove adhesive (1) not to damage primer application surface (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01950043.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.593mm" ver = "01" gw = "191" gh = "129"/>
</figure>
</attention3>
</s1>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Before using knife, degrease it with alcohol or the like.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01950042.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.482mm" ver = "01" gw = "197" gh = "132"/>
</figure>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9506002003" page = "2">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
For proper handling and drying time of primer and adhesive, refer to their maker’s instruction.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
 To determine installing position of windshield (1) to body (2), position glass against body so that clearance between upper end of windshield and body is approximately 4.0 mm (0.16 in.) and clearances between each side end (right &#38; left) of windshield and body are even.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Then put alignment marks (3) on windshield and body.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Windshield clearance
</title>
<ptxt>
“a”: Approx. 4.0 mm (0.16 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A950013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.238mm" ver = "01" gw = "226" gh = "160"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clean contact surfaces of old adhesive (4) left on body. Apply primer (2) where paint or bare metal is exposed (3).
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Do not apply primer on adhesive.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8G001950046.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "33.544mm" ver = "01" gw = "164" gh = "79"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.236in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.176in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.236in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.898in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Do not apply primer.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Body panel
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Clean area about 30 to 50 mm (1.19 to 1.96 in.) from the edge of windshield with gauze and white gasoline. Dry white gasoline for 10 minutes or more.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply primer onto windshield molding mounting area on windshield (2) and install new windshield molding (3) to windshield.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install new spacers (1) and fasteners (4) to windshield.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A950014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "60.689mm" ver = "01" gw = "147" gh = "156"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply primer to adhesive application area on windshield.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Do not touch primer-coated surface.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply adhesive (1) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Attach windshield (2) on body within 5 minutes from applying adhesive.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Use rubber sucker grip to carry glass after adhesive is applied.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<spec>
<title>
Adhesive amount and application area on windshield
</title>
<ptxt>
Width of adhesive “a”: Approx. 7.0 mm (0.28 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Height of adhesive “b”: Approx. 15.0 mm (0.59 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Application area “c”: Approx. 11.5 mm (0.45 in.), “d”: Approx. 25.0 mm (0.98 in.), “e”: Approx. 13.4 mm (0.53 in.), “f”: Approx. 34.0 mm (1.34 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A950016.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "111.086mm" ver = "01" gw = "225" gh = "298"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.236in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.274in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.236in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.748in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Windshield molding
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Spacer
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Holding windshield (3) with rubber sucker grips (1), align fasteners (2) with holes (4) of body, align alignment marks put in Step 1) and install windshield.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A950017.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "82.149mm" ver = "01" gw = "223" gh = "216"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Dry adhesive.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Open or close doors with all door glasses open until adhesive is fully hardened.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Hold windshield molding with tape until it is fixed.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not drive until adhesive is fully hardened.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for water leakage 1 or 2 hours after installing windshield. If leakage is found, remove and install windshield again.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not apply excessive water pressure during water leakage check.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH01950051.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.958mm" ver = "01" gw = "195" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not blow compressed air directly to adhesive applied part when drying.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not dry forcibly using infrared light or the like.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install head lining if it has been removed. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install instrument panel if it has been removed. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install inner rear view mirror. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9506007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install cowl top garnish. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install wiper arms. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9406003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
